Package: DO.utils
Type: Package
Title: Public Resource Utilities Designed by/for the Disease Ontology
Version: 0.3.3
Author: J. Allen Baron
Maintainer: J. Allen Baron <allenbaron@som.umaryland.edu>
Description: Generally useful tools to assess use of public resources in
    scientific literature ("cited by", search, etc.) and to simplify common R
    tasks, along with tools specifically designed for analysis and
    improvement of the Human Disease Ontology (DO; https://disease-ontology.org).
